    "The learning rate was selected to be 0.001 based on different experiments.",
    "Two scales, 0.1 and 0.1, were used to change the learning rate at two different steps that are 3200 and 3600.",
    "Finally, the max batches were set up to be 4000 as recommended in [27] (max batches = number of classes 9 2000).",
    "Also, K-means clustering was used to select the anchors' sizes based on the dataset; nine anchors were used for those experiments.",
    "Mass classificationSix experiments were conducted for classification with the same sets for training, validation, and testing that were used in detection for each dataset."
